From d41457961dec42c50cd1793cf2279dd8d088763d Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <claude@example.com>
Date: Fri, 13 Mar 2026 07:07:09 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Apply MCP best practices for registry publication

- Prefix all 32 tool names with multipass_ to avoid conflicts with other MCP servers
- Add MCP tool annotations (readOnlyHint, destructiveHint, idempotentHint, openWorldHint) to every tool
- Add human-readable title annotations (WithTitleAnnotation) to every tool
- Make version injectable at build time via -ldflags (-X main.version=...)
- Fix Dockerfile: replace broken Python-based image with multi-stage Go build
- Remove deprecated _python/ directory and smithery.yaml
- Add go install instructions to README
- Update README, CLAUDE.md, and examples to reflect new tool names
- Document tool annotations in README
